attributes.value: Bryan Brinkman is an award-winning multi-media artist who utilizes his career in animation and motion graphics to create fun and inventive ways to convey ideas that are both approachable and appealing. His work has been minted on SuperRare, NiftyGateway, ArtBlocks, and Async, as well as appearing in Christie's and Sotheby's.
